<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>[전주대학교] ${jdSurveyDefinition.name?default("")}</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;font-weight:200;font-size:17px;color:#333;letter-spacing:-0.5px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-moz-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;">
    <div style="width: 1024px; margin: 0 auto; clear: both; position: relative;">
      <div style="margin: 5% 0 1% 2%;"><img src="http://www.jj.ac.kr/www/_res/img/survey-logo.png" alt="전주대학교"></div>
      <div style="width: 90%; border: 5px solid #0078ad; border-bottom:none; margin-left: 2%; padding: 1% 3%;">
           <p style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.9em; word-break: keep-all;">
           안녕하세요!<br>
           전주대학교 <strong>${registDeptNm?default("")}</strong>입니다.<br>
           [<strong>${jdSurveyDefinition.purpose?default("")}</strong>]으로 다음과 같이 설문조사를 진행하고 있습니다.<br>
           바쁘시더라도 잠시 시간을 내주셔서 귀중한 의견을 주시면 대단히 감사하겠습니다.
         </p><br>

         <table cellspacing="0" style="width:90%; border-top:3px solid #0078ad; font-weight:200; font-size:1.4em; color:#333; margin:auto;">
          <colgroup>
              <col width="20%">
              <col width="80%">
          </colgroup>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td scope="row" style="border-right:1px solid #dedede;border-bottom:1px solid #dedede;padding:6px 10px;background:#fafafa;text-align:center;">
                설문명
              </td>
              <td style="border-bottom:1px solid #dedede;padding:6px 10px;">
                ${jdSurveyDefinition.name?default("")}
              </td>
            </tr>
              <tr>
                <td scope="row" style="border-right:1px solid #dedede;border-bottom:1px solid #dedede;padding:6px 10px;background:#fafafa;text-align:center;">
                  응답기간
                </td>
                <td style="border-bottom:1px solid #dedede;padding:6px 10px;">
                  ${startDate?default("")}.(${startDay?default("")})~${endDate?default("")}.(${endDay?default("")}) 까지
                </td>
              </tr>
          </tbody>
         </table>

            <div style="text-align:center; margin:8% auto;">
            <a href="${urlLink}" target="_blank" title="설문 응답하기 새창열기" style="font-size: 1.3em; padding:10px 25px; border:1px solid #0078ad; border-radius: 6px; background:#0078ab; color:#fff; text-decoration: none;">
              설문 응답하기<img src="http://www.jj.ac.kr/www/_res/img/btn-link.png" style="padding-left: 10px; vertical-align: -10%;"/>
            </a>
          </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#f3f3f3; margin:0 1% 0 2%; border: 5px solid #0078ad; border-top:none; padding:5px;">
        <ul>
          <li style="position: relative; font-weight: 200; font-size: 1.2em; color: #191919; line-height: 1.5em; list-style-type: none;">
            (55069) 전라북도 전주시 완산구 천잠로 303 전주대학교
          </li>
          <li style="position: relative; font-weight: 200; font-size: 1.2em; color: #191919; line-height: 1.5em; list-style-type: none;">
            TEL : <a href="tel:1577-7177" title="전화걸기" style="color: #191919; text-decoration: none;">+82-1577-7177</a> | FAX : +82-63-220-2464 | E-MAIL : <a href="mailto:webmaster@jj.ac.kr" title="메일보내기" style="color: #191919; text-decoration: none;">webmaster@jj.ac.kr</a>
          </li>
          <li style="position: relative; font-weight: 200; font-size: 1.2em; color: #191919; line-height: 1.5em; list-style-type: none;">
            Copyrights (C)2020 Jeonju University. All Rights Reserved.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
